snippet.title: Resistance 204X - Teaser Trailer (Fighting Game with Rollback Netcode)
snippet.description:
Resistance 204X on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1829140/Resistance_204X

Fight against other players locally or cross-play online on this fast-paced footsies-based 2D fighting game. Block! Poke! Jump! Grab! Hit & Confirm at the right moment. Make combos and special attacks without bleeding your thumb. Run and reach the end of the stage to win the match.

#Resistance204X #trailer #indiegames #gaming
